RECONSIDERATION DOCKET

93-1374. State v. Webb.

Clermont County, No. CA91-08-053. Reported at 70 Ohio St.3d 325, 638 N.E.2d 1203.

On motion for reconsideration. Motion denied.

On application for stay of execution pending final disposition of appeal to United States Supreme Court. Application denied.

Moyer, C.J., Douglas and Wright, JJ., dissent.
